Interface TransitSchedule

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Attributable, MatsimToplevelContainer
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    TransitScheduleImpl

    public interface TransitSchedule
extends MatsimToplevelContainer, Attributable
    Stores a complete transit schedules with multiple lines, multiple routes per line, all the time data and the infrastructure in form of stop facilities.

    mrieser
